{
  "stem": "6777.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just told you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I haven't been in any primary school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Home tuition for a couple of years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And straight to the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From first-- I've been nine-- to year eight, when I've been six and 1/2, 16 and 1/2, nearly 17.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents believed that two, the first two years can be taught at home, and especially since the home was a bilingual one.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We've been taught both languages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German and Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There have been very few Jewish girls in the gymna-- it was an all-girl school, of course.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There have been very few Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because as you probably know, the Polish government didn't like to have in the government schools many Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a Jewish gymnasium in Kalisz, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And most of the Jewish children, if they ever came to the gymnasium, they went to the Jewish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they have not gained the entrances to the government one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it wasn't numerus clausus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a test.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the way of not letting them in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there always has been a few who have been so good that they had to be accepted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There has usually been one or two in each of the classes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes and no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not generally, but now and again, you could feel it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not officially.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know how to answer this question.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, for the first education after the middle, after gymnasium-- or as you call it today, high school-- the universities.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you came from a state school, you had a much easier entrance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From the Jewish gymnasium, it was much harder to get into university.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's number one.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
